text:
i have had tiktok since 2019, great app to waste time but other than that there really is nothing else. after a while everything gets repetitive and boring. the constant inbox updates are annoying as well as the guidelines. nothing wrong with the actual guidelines themselves just the way they are so flimsy about them. a creator with a large enough following will get away with just about anything but if you have a smaller following they will find just about any reason to ban/find something wrong with your videos/account.

 i DO NOT recommend getting this app for anyone UNDER the age of 13-14 if you are considering getting this app for your child who is under that age PLEASE DO NOT. there are things on there that they should not be seeing/be exposed to that young. such as porn/nudity, constant negativity, politic wars, body checking, ED promotion, toxic beauty/body standards, SH, gore and much much more. not only that it tends to have an effect of making them grow up too quickly.

 if you are above/around 13-14 or older i would recommend , it is great to help pass time as well as to keep yourself entertained (if it doesnâ€™t get repetitive of course)
